<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_4ee438cabb4a.aspx"><b>雨后池上</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e5%88%98%e6%94%bd">刘攽</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson4ee438cabb4a">
一雨池塘水面平，淡磨明镜照檐楹。<br />东风忽起垂杨舞，更作荷心万点声。
</div>
</div>
