<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_cb181f3fe002.aspx"><b>画鸭</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%83%e4%bb%a3">元代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e6%8f%ad%e5%82%92%e6%96%af">揭傒斯</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsoncb181f3fe002">
春草细还生，春雏养渐成。<br />茸茸毛色起，应解自呼名。
</div>
